    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors not formally assessed are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. Discretization error (2.1% GCI) and experimental comparison (8.3% MAE) both within acceptance criteria. RH < 1 criterion satisfied across all 5 operating points. Turbulence model sensitivity bounded at 4.7%. Overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory decision for this Class II CPB device.",
